                        </div>
                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<table style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%; font-family:Monospace;font-size: 10pt;">
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%; background-color: silver;" rowspan="75"></th>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;">EVENT NAME:</th>
<td style="border: 1px solid black;" rowspan="10">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:xx-large;"><tt>FACTORY</tt></span><br />
<tt>(EST. 1835)</tt></p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">Negotiation In Response To Sabotage</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;">EVENT ID:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">N-58711</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;">IMPORTANCE:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">High</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;">LOCATION:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">Fort Cass, Eastern Tennessee Manufacturing Center<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;">DATE:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">January 6, 2002</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;" colspan="2">PRIMARY ACTOR(S):</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%" colspan="2">
<ul>
<li>Unknown Organization Negotiator The Questioner</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;" colspan="2">PRIMARY FACTORY ACTOR:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%" colspan="2">
<ul>
<li>The Investor<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-2')">2</a></sup></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;" colspan="2">OTHER PARTICIPATING FACTORY ACTORS:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%" colspan="2">
<ul>
<li>Elder Foreman Robert Henegar<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-3')">3</a></sup></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;" colspan="2">OTHER AFFECTED STAKEHOLDERS:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%" colspan="2">
<ul>
<li>Factory Customers In The Eastern Tennessee Region And Sub-Regions</li>
<li>Factory Stock Holders</li>
<li>All Personnel Assets At The Fort Cass Location</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;" colspan="2">RELEVANT PRIOR INFORMATION:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%" colspan="2">The as yet unidentified group represented by The Questioner has a history of sabotage and attempted hostile takeover with The Factory. This stems from what appears to be a difference of opinion on resource management. On November 13, 2001 this unidentified group began a series of sabotages against Factory assets at the Fort Cass location.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;" colspan="2">DESCRIPTION:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%" colspan="2">Evidence of sabotage was detected within the Factory location. After a period of escalated conflict, The Questioner appeared within the Factory. After a series of negotiations, it was determined that the potential cost of retaining the Fort Cass location was higher than the profits to be made.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;" colspan="2">TRIGGER:</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%" colspan="2">Upon the appearance of The Questioner, The Board of Directors dispatched The Investor to conduct emergency negotiations.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;" colspan="2">ORDER OF EVENTS</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%"><strong>Actor Action</strong></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%"><strong>Factory Response</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Questioner was last observed near the base of the <em>Nyssa sylvatica</em> instance at the center of The Factory.</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Investor enters the Factory alone as any misstep or misspoken word could result in a breakdown of negotiation.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Questioner does not leave their position at the base of the <em>Nyssa sylvatica</em> as basic etiquette would generally dictate. In fact, The Questioner does not acknowledge the presence of The Investor.</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Investor had been appropriately briefed before leaving for negotiation and shows no reaction to The Questioner's rude behavior. As well, The Investor restrains himself from conducting any typically suitable greeting.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-4" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-4')">4</a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%"></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Investor carefully travels the structurally unsound floor of Primary Production Level 1.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%"></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">Upon his arrival, The Investor makes great efforts to neither observe nor acknowledge The Questioner. While carefully studying a section of exposed rebar, The Investor speaks.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-5" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-5')">5</a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Questioner moves closer to The Investor, washing the area in the scent of moss and damp earth.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-6" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-6')">6</a></sup></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Investor tenses, but does not move away. He bends to examine a fleck of fallen rust upon the root of the <em>Nyssa sylvatica</em>.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-7" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-7')">7</a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Questioner turns and descends through a gap in the broken floor.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-8" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-8')">8</a></sup> The broken floor had formed a basin that was filled with clean, pure water.</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Investor produces a copy of a contract establishing terms of a cease of hostility between all present parties.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-9" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-9')">9</a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Questioner takes the contract and carelessly drops it into the basin of water.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-10" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-10')">10</a></sup></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Investor moves suddenly to seize The Questioner before finding his movement impaired.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-11" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-11')">11</a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%"></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Investor is compelled to descend into the basin of water.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-12" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-12')">12</a></sup> As his feet enter the water, he makes eye contact with his reflection and sinks slowly into the water.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-13" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-13')">13</a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%">The Questioner turns away and disappears from the Factory.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-14" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-14')">14</a></sup></td>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: silver;" colspan="2">RESULTS/FOLLOW UP</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 0 1%" colspan="2">A retrieval team was sent into The Factory after a period of 24 hours, 47 minutes, 12 second with no contact from The Investor. The Investor was found seated upon a slab of fallen concrete and was escorted away from The Factory.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-15" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-15')">15</a></sup><br />
For further context to this event, reference <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/eco-sabotage-s-67789/offset/0">Document S-67789</a>.</td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class="footnotes-footer">
<div class="title">Footnotes</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-1')">1</a>. Location ID: MC-1533609-ET</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-2')">2</a>. Foreman ID: INV00000001</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-3"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-3')">3</a>. Foreman ID: ELD00000007</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-4"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-4')">4</a>. Ex Post Facto:<br />
<blockquote>
<p>A shearing, screeching, building to a pitch outside of human hearing.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-5"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-5')">5</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>Squeaking and grinding, like that of a hinge on a seldom used door.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-6"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-6')">6</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>The silence of a glade in springtime.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-7"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-7')">7</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>Clicking, then whirring, followed by the sound of a far off pneumatic press.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-8"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-8')">8</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>The silence after a hammer strikes, after machinery powers off, and of the absence of industry.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-9"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-9')">9</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>Gurgling as oil and blood are forced through a piston.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-10"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-10')">10</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>The silence of a predator stalking its prey.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-11"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-11')">11</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>The grinding and tearing of limbs caught between gears.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-12"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-12')">12</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>The crash of mechanical failure.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-13"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-13')">13</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>A hiss, steam escaping a sealed gasket.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-14"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-14')">14</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>The silence of acquiescence and sacrifice.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-15"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-15')">15</a>.
<blockquote>
<p>The gurgling of an empty fuel reservoir. The echo of hammer strikes in an infinitely long tunnel.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
